featured_reviews.response_from_owner_text:
Hello Michelle.

I would like to thank you for being a return customer to our stores.  We really appreciate your business and look forward to helping you in the future.

Due to the nationwide issues with shoplifting and organized theft rings that target businesses like ours, the ban on large bags has become a necessity. Without it we would not be able to maintain our competitive pricing and stock availability for paying customers.

Since it may be interpreted as discriminatory for us to take some customers bags and not others, we unfortunately have to make the rule applicable to all bags that are over a certain size.  

Please know that we very much look forward to a day when this will no longer be needed. 

Our locations are monitored at all times and we do background checks on all staff so that we are able to assure the safety of any items that remain behind the counter.

We are sorry that you felt scolded for wanting to have someone accompany you to the dressing room and we will review that experience and see if there are any training issues that we can address to help with that messaging in the future.  While this is a policy that remains, we hope that there can be kinder communication in the future on this. What most customers do in these instances is crack the door slightly to allow a shopping buddy to give them some feedback.

We very much appreciate you taking the time and effort to provide us with the above feedback and want to again thank you very much for your business - past, present, and, hopefully, future.

Merhaba Michelle.

Magazalarimiza tekrar gelen musterimiz oldugunuz icin tesekkur ederim. Isinizi gercekten takdir ediyoruz ve gelecekte size yardimci olmayi sabirsizlikla bekliyoruz.

Lokasyonlarimiz her zaman izleniyor ve tezgahin arkasinda kalan esyalarin guvenligini saglayabilmek icin tum personelin gecmisini kontrol ediyoruz.

Birisinin size soyunma odasina kadar eslik etmesini istediginiz icin azarlandiginiz icin uzgunuz ve bu deneyimi gozden gecirecegiz ve gelecekte bu mesaja yardimci olmak icin cozebilecegimiz herhangi bir egitim sorunu olup olmadigina bakacagiz. Yukaridaki geri bildirimleri bize saglamak icin zaman ve caba ayirdiginiz icin cok tesekkur ederiz ve gecmisteki, simdiki ve umarim gelecekteki isiniz icin size tekrar cok tesekkur etmek isteriz.
